; REMARKS: single-impl: devirtualized a call to _ZN1A1nEi
; SKIP-REMARKS-NOT: single-impl

; Check that backend does not fail generating native code.
; RUN: %clang_cc1 -triple x86_64-grtev4-linux-gnu \
